== 反響 ==

=== 評價 ===

《換腦行動》獲得多為負面的評價。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度31%<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/criminal_2016/ |title=Criminal (2016) |website=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=April 16, 2016 |archive-date=2021-01-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210128204412/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/criminal_2016 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]得分37<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/criminal-2016 | title=Criminal reviews | website=Metacritic | accessdate=April 16, 2016 | archive-date=2020-11-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112021617/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/criminal-2016 | dead-url=no }}</ref>，普遍不受專業影評人認同。據[[CinemaScore|CinemaScore]]調查，觀眾的評價在A+至F之間給了本片「B」，觀眾反應較好<ref name="CinemaScore">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/04/the-jungle-book-barbershop-the-next-cut-criminal-late-nights-thursday-box-office-1201738263/|title=Matinees Solid After ‘The Jungle Book’s $4.2M, ‘Barbershop: The Next Cut’s $735K — Friday Box Office|work=deadline.com|access-date=2016-04-19|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211235911/https://deadline.com/2016/04/the-jungle-book-barbershop-the-next-cut-criminal-late-nights-thursday-box-office-1201738263/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
電影在北美票房總額為1470萬美元，其他地區2100萬美元，全球總計3480萬美元<ref name=TheNumbers/>。

在美國和加拿大，根據估計，《換腦行動》約能在首映週末中從2,683劇院收穫900-1200萬美元，僅次於《[[與森林共舞|與森林共舞]]》（6700-7500萬美元）及《{{link-en|哈啦大髮師3|Barbershop: The Next Cut}}》（2700-3000萬美元）<ref name="BB">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/04/the-jungle-book-barbershop-the-next-cut-criminal-box-office-preview-1201736035/|title=‘The Jungle Book’, ‘Barbershop: The Next Cut’ To Ignite Weekend Box Office – Preview|author=Anita Busch and Nancy Tartaglione|work=''[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]''|date=April 12, 2016|accessdate=April 13, 2016|archive-date=2016-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160529014320/https://deadline.com/2016/04/the-jungle-book-barbershop-the-next-cut-criminal-box-office-preview-1201736035/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美國首週末票房收入為580萬美元，位居當週第六，表現不甚理想，同時也是主演[[凱文·科斯納|凱文·科斯納]]生涯票房最低的第八名<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/box-office-jon-favreaus-jungle-883622|title=Box Office: Jon Favreau's 'Jungle Book' Swings to Stellar $4.2M Thursday Night|author=Pamela McClintock|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=April 15, 2016|accessdate=April 17, 2016}}</ref>。

